<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: #212529; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a5276, #1e8449); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .header h1 { color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
    .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin: 8px 0 0; }
    .body { background: white; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
    .items-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
    .items-table th { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6; }
    .items-table td { padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #f39c12; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Nuevo pedido recibido</h1>
      <p>Panel de Administración — CB Tomelloso</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Se ha realizado un nuevo pedido en la tienda:</p>

      <p><strong>Pedido:</strong> {{orderNumber}}<br>
      <strong>Cliente:</strong> {{customerName}}<br>
      <strong>Email:</strong> {{customerEmail}}<br>
      <strong>Total:</strong> {{totalAmount}}</p>

      <table class="items-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Producto</th><th>Cant.</th><th>Subtotal</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {{#each items}}
          <tr><td>{{this.productName}}</td><td>{{this.quantity}}</td><td>{{this.subtotal}} €</td></tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <br>
      <a href="{{adminUrl}}" class="btn">Gestionar pedido</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>CB Tomelloso — Panel de Administración</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
